<lyrics>[V1]
 1- msẖ qạdr ạ̉kẖd qrạry
 wbạ̹yd ạgẖmy ʿnyạ dạymạ
 swʾ ạkẖtyạry mạlk ʿly̱ qlby fyạ
 ʿạysẖ ạ̉nạ bwsẖyn mqswm ạ̉nạ lạtnyn
 nṣ lkẖṭyty w ạltạny lyạ
 ạlqrạr - (ạ̉nạ msẖ bḥạsb nfsy ʿly̱ ḥạjẗ mạʿmlthạsẖ
 mạnạ ʿạrf ạ̹ny kẖạṭy w ạ̹n byn ạlnạs mạswạsẖ
 qlqy wkẖwfy mktfny w mkẖlyny tmly rkẖyṣ
 lkn yswʿ sẖạyfny gẖạly wkmạn qdys)2
 2- lw mhmạ tzyd jrwḥy w tmwt ạlfrḥẗ fyạ
 yswʿ hạyrd rwḥy w yrjʿ frḥy lyạ
 qlby mn qbrh yqwm lmạ ynạdyny fy ywm
 w fy mḥnty ạ̹ydh tsnd ạ̹ydyạ</lyrics>
<title>qrạry</title>
</song>